These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: lemon, plum, spinach
City: marseilles, prague, boston
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, d&b, dubstep
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, orange, blood-red
 1. the person who likes green is the german##1
 2. the person who likes blood-red is the mechanic##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the italian and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the designer is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person traveling to boston is the colombian##1
 7. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the person who likes orange is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the person who likes green is on the left of the designer##1
10. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Food          | plum       | spinach    | lemon         |
| City         | prague    | boston  | marseilles        |
| Job           | accountant | designer   | mechanic      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | dubstep    | country       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Color         | green     | orange | blood-red |

