.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, sprite
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, jet-ski, snowmobile
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, punk, rock
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, sunflower, tulip
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the owner of the pony is the person who growssunflower##1
 2. the owner of the pony is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the fan of metal##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the fan of rock##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | sprite    | juice         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Transport   | skateboard  | snowmobile  | jet-ski     |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | punk      | metal         |
| Flower   | tulip      | sunflower   | zinnia    |
| Pet           | dog        | pony      | horse         |
| Sport         | water-polo | baseball  | weightlifting |

