 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the musician is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the person drinking milk is between the musician and the social-worker##2
10. the modern house is on the left of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
