The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, taxi, van
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in the middle##1
 2. the person eating kale is in the middle##1
 3. the polish is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the person eating strawberry and the american##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is the person driving the subway##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person driving the subway is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food      | strawberry | kale      | papaya      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| Birthday   | december | february  | july |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | polish     | american |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Sport         | handball    | water-polo | soccer   |
| Transport     | taxi        | van        | subway   |

