.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, tea
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, old-henry, swisher
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman, nurse
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, french, italian
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, rabbit
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, baking, writing
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
1. the person drinking milk is the swisher-smoker##1
2. the person driving the roller is the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the dressmaker is between the person drinking tea and the owner of the rabbit##2
4. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the fisherman is the davidoff-smoker##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the french is between the davidoff-smoker and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | milk       | tea      |
| Cigar          | davidoff   | swisher   | old-henry  |
| Job           | fisherman  | dressmaker | nurse    |
| Nationality   | canadian   | french     | italian  |
| Pet           | rabbit     | dog        | hedgehog |
| Hobby         | baking | camping   | writing  |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | roller     | car      |

 